&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We are seeking an Account Manager for the New York City office. The main objective of this position is to partner with clients to execute GMG’s custom content campaigns. The Account Manager will manage the entire campaign lifecycle, operationalizing internal teams to ensure brand goals and expectations are met - while providing best in class client relationship management. The Account Manager partners with the sales, influencer, design, editorial, production, product and marketing teams to manage the production, creative and performance goals surrounding campaigns. The Account Manager is responsible for building revenue and driving results in order to maintain customer retention.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
