&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Operate as the lead client point of contact for robust branded content programs to ensure successful execution of the campaign&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;GMG ambassador for brand and campaign success&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Work in conjunction with sales and brand strategy teams to gain a clear understanding of clients’ goals and objectives pre-campaign launch&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Create and maintain all campaign documentation (including Kick off Call decks, production timelines, budget trackers, etc…)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Orchestrate internal teams and third party vendors to ensure a timely execution of all client and campaign deliverables&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Develop production timelines and manage execution for custom programs, often first-of-their-kind&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Frequently communicate with clients, providing them with relevant updates, assets for approval and performance recommendations&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
